  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0002",
      "text": " 132",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0003",
      "text": "5",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.38,
        102.1,
        69.64
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0004",
      "text": "FC-4 Link Service",
      "bbox": [
        114.0,
        57.38,
        206.21,
        69.64
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0005",
      "text": "An FC-4 Link Service request solicits a destination Port (Fx_Port or Nx_Port) to perform a function or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        540.05,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0006",
      "text": "service in order to support an individual FC-4 Device_Data protocol.  The Information Category for a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        540.04,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0007",
      "text": "request shall be specified as Unsolicited Control.  A FC-4 Link Service reply may be transmitted in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.95,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0008",
      "text": "answer to a FC-4 Link Service request.  The Information Category for a reply shall be specified as",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.99,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0009",
      "text": "Solicited Control.  Each request or reply shall be composed of a single Sequence.  The format of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.0,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0010",
      "text": "request or reply shall be specified by the individual FC-4 being supported and is beyond the scope of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.97,
        540.04,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0011",
      "text": "this standard.  Each Sequence may be composed of one or more frames.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        420.31,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0012",
      "text": "The protocols supported by the FC-4 Link Services shall be performed within a single Exchange, in-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.07,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0013",
      "text": "tended exclusively for the purpose.  FC-4 Link Service protocols are performed using a two Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.14,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0014",
      "text": "quence Exchange.  The protocols consist of a request Sequence by the Originator (Nx_Port), transfer",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        540.03,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0015",
      "text": "of Sequence Initiative (see FC-FS-2), and a reply Sequence from the Responder (Nx_Port or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.96,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0016",
      "text": "Fx_Port).  The execution of a FC-4 Link Service may perform sequence abort functions and modify",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        539.92,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0017",
      "text": "sequence initiative of other exchanges in a protocol specific manner.  The Sequence Initiator and Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        539.94,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0018",
      "text": "quence Recipient shall follow the rules for Sequence management and Recovery_Qualifier reuse as",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.07,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0019",
      "text": "specified in FC-FS-2.  The following rules regarding Sequence and Exchange management apply to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        539.95,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0020",
      "text": "FC-4 Link Services in addition to the rules specified in FC-FS-2:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        377.56,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0021",
      "text": "a) FC-4 Link Services shall only be Exchanges originated following N_Port Login.",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        298.96,
        469.5,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0022",
      "text": "b) the Originator of the Exchange shall use the Discard multiple Sequences Exchange Error Poli-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        322.96,
        540.01,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0023",
      "text": "cy (see FC-FS-2) for all FC-4 Link Service Exchanges.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        334.96,
        363.41,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0024",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        358.96,
        114.35,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0025",
      "text": "the Originator of an FC-4 Link Service Exchange shall detect an Exchange error following Se-",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        358.96,
        540.15,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0026",
      "text": "quence Initiative transfer if the reply Sequence is not received within a timeout interval equal to",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        370.96,
        539.89,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0027",
      "text": "twice the value of R_A_TOV.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        382.96,
        250.63,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0028",
      "text": "d) if the Exchange Originator of an FC-4 Link Service Exchange detects an Exchange error, it",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        406.96,
        540.03,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0029",
      "text": "shall abort the Exchange using ABTS and retry the protocol of the aborted Exchange with a dif-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        540.12,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0030",
      "text": "ferent Exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.96,
        197.97,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0031",
      "text": "e) if the Sequence Initiator aborts a Sequence using ABTS (Abort Sequence Protocol) due to re-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        454.96,
        540.07,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0032",
      "text": "ceiving an ACK with the Abort Sequence bits (5-4) set to 01b, the Sequence Initiator shall re-try",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        466.96,
        539.96,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0033",
      "text": "the Sequence after the Basic Accept (see FC-FS-2) is received for the aborted Sequence one",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        478.96,
        540.02,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0034",
      "text": "time only.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        490.96,
        165.11,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0035",
      "text": "R_CTL bits 31-28 (Word 0) are set = to 0011b to indicate a FC-4 Link_Data frame.  The TYPE field",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.94,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0036",
      "text": "for each FC-4 Link Service frame shall match the FC-4 Device_Data TYPE field as specified in FC-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        540.0,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p151_s0037",
      "text": "FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        120.43,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}